ilog.cplex

Class IloCplex.BooleanParam

  • java.lang.Object
    • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.Param
      • ilog.cplex.IloCplex.BooleanParam
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Enclosing class:
    IloCplex

    public static class IloCplex.BooleanParam
extends IloCplex.Param
    Symbolic names for parameters in IloCplex that are Boolean-valued. Boolean values are sometimes also referred to as binary values or zero-one values. For more detail about each parameter, see the CPLEX Parameters Reference Manual.
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
